# Hardware

Webconverger works with **almost any standard x86 hardware** that meets
[Firefox's minimum
requirements](http://www.mozilla.com/en-US/firefox/system-requirements.html).
However there are some interesting mini PC hardware options available, such as:

* [[Koolu,_Linutop_and_interPC|mpc]]


